{
  "stem": "19939.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 103.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Later, I realized that he probably announced them that he is getting married again.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Was three years after.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they were against it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I don't know why, what it-- what this-- this-- I don't know milieu was that something that there might be in these Jewish circles that she didn't want him to remarry, you know?",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But he had two children, right?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He needed somebody.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He had-- he lived there in this Debica with his brother who helped him in business.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they had the housekeeper.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was never told about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I realized that this must have been.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was just pleading.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so I know that he got-- he remarried.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He married a young woman, 21 years old.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she must have been from a not well-to-do family because otherwise, she wouldn't have married a widower with two children.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I am-- I mention this because this is how it was, these mores.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There's such a provincial way of life, you know, in Poland, that mentioning about that she was poor or something, you know, I have to-- I must mention it here.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "People, the President are proud of their poor background, right, what the parents achieved.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And in Poland was just the opposite.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then we know that there were so many geniuses among the poor people that never had a chance to-- to-- to develop because, you know.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So anyhow, so I was there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I was going to school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First, I was going to school in this little town, right, for three years, the third grade.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This Ropczyce where my, you know, know mother's parents lived, where I was stayed the three years after my mother died.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "R-O-P-C-Z-Y-C-E.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was there going to school, was a very good student.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
